<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Döner, kumpir, lahmacun, balık ekmek ve midye dolma gibi lezzetler Türkiye&#8217;de mutlaka denemeniz gereken sokak yemekleridir.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-03-07T18:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:38:52Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'tr' AND "slug" = 'turkiyede-gida-guvenligi-sokak-yemekleri' );
